Titolo: Mega Apocalypse

Anno: 1987

Descrizione: Mega Apocalypse is a multidirectional shooter written by Simon Nicol for the Commodore 64 and ported to the BBC Micro, Amstrad CPC, and ZX Spectrum. It is the sequel to Crazy Comets. Both games are clones of Gottlieb's 1983 arcade game Mad Planets. The music is by Rob Hubbard.

